00:39:39.100 --> 00:39:40.300
Right, go.

00:39:40.300 --> 00:39:47.340
Loose wood? Never good.

00:39:50.290 --> 00:39:53.970
Inspector 34 showed us how perfect life could be.

00:39:54.610 --> 00:40:01.360
