Wow, how about a game of kick the can?

00:40:48.480 --> 00:40:48.720
Me?

00:40:49.600 --> 00:40:50.640
Sure thing.

00:40:50.640 --> 00:40:54.720
Just close your eyes and count to 10 while we tear butt and kick the can.

00:40:55.600 --> 00:40:56.160
What the hey?

00:40:57.840 --> 00:41:00.080
Only if I might make a suggestion.

00:41:00.960 --> 00:41:04.720
Perhaps the game would be more efficiently played in teams with boundaries.

00:41:04.720 --> 00:41:06.080
Say the end of the yard.

00:41:06.080 --> 00:41:08.320
Perhaps a set game time would streamline things.

00:41:08.880 --> 00:41:09.920
Why don't we think of that?

00:41:11.280 --> 00:41:16.080
I'm trained to catch defects before they become defeats.

00:41:16.080 --> 00:41:18.560
Come on, Shatterheads. Let's play can.

00:41:19.120 --> 00:41:25.010
Inspector 34 had jumped off the sideline.

00:41:25.010 --> 00:41:29.410
Not only was he learning to live, he's learning to make life better.

00:41:29.410 --> 00:41:32.050
Thanks to his amazing powers of perfection.

00:41:35.730 --> 00:41:40.690
Maybe the best thing of all, he was finally beginning to learn that being perfect

00:41:42.290 --> 00:41:44.130
