00:42:26.290 --> 00:42:26.530
No.

00:42:27.730 --> 00:42:32.530
I used to look at all the flaws in the world and I'd think if I could make one thing perfect.

00:42:33.650 --> 00:42:34.290
And then I did.

00:42:35.170 --> 00:42:35.810
Underpants.

00:42:36.850 --> 00:42:38.530
